<H1>V. Summary</H1>
Besides the references mentioned at the end of the chapter, I found two URLs
that may be worth looking at.  (Note: my intention was to find sites that 
provided demos of the applications discussed, and I was only successful
in finding something about PaperVideo.)
<BR>
<UL>
<LI>
