</LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="http://hil.ntt.co.jp/avp/PaperVideo/paper.html">PaperVideo</A>
 This is only in Japanese :-), but there is a descriptive picture and a link
to download a QuickTime file of a PaperVideo demonstration. 
